    "body": "@benjaminmbrown We've just started publishing an experimental build - truffle@byoc - which automatically pulls down any compiler you'd like from solc-bin. You just have to set a key in the `truffle.js` config specifying the version. \r\n\r\n[Usage docs](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle-compile/tree/byoc-docs#truffle-compiler)\r\n\r\n**Install**\r\n```\r\nnpm install -g truffle@byoc\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt's current with `4.1.12` - please report its bugs :)",
